gltfjsx v6 is out today. the tool turns models into declarative JSX.
for a while now the --transform flag compressed your assets, in v6 it compresses the hell out of it using gltf-transform by @donrmccurdy (draco, prune, webp & squoosh). it could turn a 100mb glb into kb's. https://t.co/X3CeVTvy4z
